result.title: DaVita Marks 25 Years of Innovation with Breakthrough Kidney Care Research at ASN Kidney Week 2025
result.text: Six new studies from DaVita Clinical Research spotlight improved outcomes with GLP-1 use, advancements in treatments, transplant access and end-of-life care DENVER and HOUSTON , Nov. 4, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- DaVita, a steadfast leader in kidney care research and innovation, is unveiling six new studies at the American Society of Nephrology's (ASN) Kidney Week 2025, taking place Nov. 5-9 in Houston, Texas.
